Azerblood are a type of Planetouched, the descendents of dwarves and Azer. They typically live by themselves or in enclaves in dwarven communiities. They resemble dwarves with metallic skin, red hair, and eyes with fiery shifting colors. They tend to be lawful neutral. They are somewhat resistant to fire, and can heat metal with their innate magic.
Source: "Legacies of Ancient Empires" by Eric L. Boyd, in Dragon #350.